          "text": "SUM",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " function and a "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "GROUP BY",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " clause. The logic is simple, with no joins, subqueries, or complex calculations. The view references a single table, which further reduces its complexity."
        }
